                    <p>BUH is a class registration system that aims for a simple and intuitive experience. Click the link below to try out BUH for yourself.</p>
                <h4>Testing</h4>
                    <p>
                        While testing HUB you will assume the role of a student registering for classes. Please take note and report any design features which you liked or disliked. If something did not make sense, please let us know by following the link below to our issues page. 
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Most importantly, if you encounter errors or features not working correctly, please submit a report with as much information as you can provide (what you were trying to accomplish, what went wrong, etc)
                        and screenshots if possible.
                    </p>
                <h4>Features</h4>
                    <p>
                        BUH currently supports the following features for use and testing:<br />
                        Login authentication<br />
                        Class search<br />
                        Class registration (add/drop classes)<br />
                        Student Dashboard with Calendar<br />
                    <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="/SignIn">To BUH (I already have a BUH account.) &raquo;</a>
                </p>
                <p>
